{"tid":2086910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建立新香港呢五個字真係見一次笑一次","createTime":"2020-06-30T13:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T14:48:25.000Z","uid":40867,"like":18,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c094df1262baf5ee6f136fd6f48ab17b67a336c0","tid":2086910,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"所謂人血饅頭嘅極致<br />\n就係希望國安法加快加辣 等bno平權機會快d黎<br />\n然後去英國海外抗爭<br />\n建立新香港 哇！！<br />\n聽到都硬硬地<br />\n<br />\n隔離post仲話咩追求更好生活乃人之常情 唔怪得人離開香港<br />\n聽到眼都突埋<br />\n莫非藍絲港豬們反對社運就唔會想有佢地心目中嘅更好生活？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咩鬧人啊？<br />\n定其實你嘅生活先係生活 其他人追求就唔啱 就自私呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩走得就走好過攬住一齊死<br />\n攬炒攬左去大西洋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n71叫我出你就同我講多我一個好多？？<br />\n你移民少你一個就同我講呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要攞流亡手足黎幫自己護航<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知醜嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己知自己事啦 建立新香港我見一次就笑一次<br />\n其實唔係話唔比你走 到時候要走都阻止唔到你<br />\n不過唔該你唔好講埋曬d咩走左仲會幫香港啊<br />\n幫其他人走個d廢話 香港人係香港嘅貢獻你有目共睹<br />\n無啦啦去左英國就會勁左？<br />\n宜家叫你幫湄公河簽名都唔夠數啊 <br />\n係香港叫捐蘋果 612 立場都牙痛咁款<br />\n人地仲要成日唔夠錢告急<br />\n咁嘅行動力同我講係英國會建立到新香港 <br />\n可以做海外抗爭基地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣同d靚仔對啊媽講話買部新電腦俾佢成績就會好有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如我等你啊 到時候我再過去lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係五毛熱狗黑警PR大陸仔葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求block<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9595ffa31407526504796adbb023cb6e8058d2","tid":2086910,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"聽日聽你高見"},{"pid":"de77c54df0c45b45b5184b3b16b7272df89593b1","tid":2086910,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0vodRn.png&amp;h=bffec503&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z74Hva5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ74Hva5.png&h=a1d38e47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"347fe3682da4a608581521580ce14c544c41aa67","tid":2086910,"uid":40867,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3d9595ffa31407526504796adbb023cb6e8058d2","tid":2086910,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"聽日聽你高見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"冇高見<br />\n不嬲都支持平權<br />\n比有需要嘅真手足走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係比班連登師係度佔便宜做蝗蟲"},{"pid":"b51b36cc636c52248884d89d573d216717b41dfe","tid":2086910,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:14:00.000Z","msg":"海外新香港=唐人街"},{"pid":"5006135264f2933290d6c3ec08fbfead3f9f66f6","tid":2086910,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:14:36.000Z","msg":"有得做英豬，邊個想做港奴"},{"pid":"a885e15baad631bbbb08040faf1bf7866a9afd96","tid":2086910,"uid":40867,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5006135264f2933290d6c3ec08fbfead3f9f66f6","tid":2086910,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:14:36.000Z","msg":"有得做英豬，邊個想做港奴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:17:05.000Z","msg":"講得冇錯<br />\n<br />\n直接認想做英豬一定好過係度扮撚曬嘢話移民係為了海外抗議/建立新香港呢d廢話"},{"pid":"b9ac86b94794990d10ebbe4fa39b6859168c1c29","tid":2086910,"uid":40867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"負評數追上正評了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解唔直接回擊我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留句樓主on9都好啊"},{"pid":"decb